### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:5000/api/categories HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get category by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/categories/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Post category
POST http://localhost:5000/api/categories HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "test"
}

### Put category
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/categories HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 16,
  "title": "test Put",
  "description": "test Put"
}

### Delete category
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/categories/15 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json